                <h1>Can You Apply Wallpaper on Textured Walls?</h1>
                <p>Wallpaper can adhere to textured walls, but success varies based on texture and wallpaper type. Textured surfaces can challenge proper adhesion, causing bubbling or peeling. To optimize results, use thicker wallpapers or consider prep work like smoothing surfaces. Proper installation techniques make a significant difference in longevity.</p>
